This directory contains Astro-H mission-specific tasks (applications).
These specific to the SXS instrument.

mxstime - calculate TIME and GTI for MXS LED on/off columns

sxsflagpix - flag SXS pixels based on Antico, electrical and recoil cross-talk,
             and MXS state

sxspi - calculate PI column from UPI and energy drift correction table

sxssamcnt - compute SampleCnt columns in SXS event and HK files needed for the
            time assignment (ahtime tool)

sxssecid - identify and group secondary events with their primaries

sxsupi - calculate UPI column from PHA using gain functions stored in CALDB
